{
  "stem": "17515.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lageralteste number one, Bruno.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And lageralteste number two, Leo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was three rules, only was [INAUDIBLE] to SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Those civilian-- civilian prisoner, they-- they could do whatever they wanted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The kapo work on the commando, on the work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was ?] kapo they calling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Soon, I started to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First I work in a-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in the commando.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I work in a commando, separate to the houses, because on periphery Auschwitz, I believe 40 to 60 kilometers square.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think people who live in beautiful houses have to leave the houses, and they move out or put them in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the houses was beautiful, beautiful, beautiful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Most of the rich people before the war lived in-- in [INAUDIBLE] Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to break it into pieces and make it even ground so-- so it could be observed-- what you call it-- make better view.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that was my-- I work for the commando.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was, I don't know, a couple-- a couple thousand people been working at different houses, different [INAUDIBLE] place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every day, after that, everyday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I hear that people come, not only from Poland, France Jewish, from France, French people, from Belgium, Holland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Auschwitz was, I tell you, Auschwitz was very important.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- there was-- like-- like in a plan made already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Auschwitz as excellent transportation from-- from entire Europe to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even from Moscow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They made a special truck, because Moscow-- a Russian truck-- truck is much wider.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they made it from Moscow to-- to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Better connection.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1940, Auschwitz was impossible to-- to be alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some people, intelligent, get crazy, get emotion, not stable, mostly intelligent people, like a professor, scientist, doctor, in two or three weeks, they get really crazy.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
